The '''International Legal English Certificate (ILEC)''' was a high-level [[English language]] qualification for [[lawyer]]s.  The ILEC exam was discontinued in December 2016.<ref>http://www.cambridgeenglish.org/exams/ilec-discontinued/</ref>

